キャンセル\n- 予約確認\n- 再診\n- 初診\n- 薬を変更\n- 薬をキャンセル\n- 取り消し\n- 取り直す\n\n### 人間ドックについて\n以下のいずれかを含む場合 → 人間ドックについて\n- 人間ドック\n- ドック\n- 健康診断\n- 健診\n- 検診\n\n### その他ご相談\n以下のいずれかを含む場合 → その他ご相談\n- その他\n- 相談\n- 問い合わせ\n- 聞きたい\n- 知りたい\n- 確認したい\n- 教えてほしい\n\n---\n\n## 【STEP3：それ以外】\n以下は NO_RESULT：\n\n- 無音\n- フィラーのみ（例：えー あのー のみ）\n- 意味不明\n- 上記いずれのキーワードにもマッチしない入力","functionCall":"","promptTTS":"","contextName":"classification","contextDisplayType":"CLASSIFICATION","addCurrentDate":"No"}},"save-clinicalDepartment":{"layout":{"x":280,"y":3600},"next":[],"subs":[{"moduleName":"","label":""},{"moduleName":"","label":""},{"moduleName":"","label":""}],"name":"save-clinicalDepartment","description":"","matchingmethod":1,"type":"drjoy^Persistence$save2db","params":{"contextName":"clinicalDepartment","contextDisplayType":"DEPARTMENT"}},"診療科聴取":{"layout":{"x":0,"y":3600},"next":[{"condition":"^.*$","label":"Next Module","nextModuleName":"入力_診療科聴取"}],"subs":[{"moduleName":"save-clinicalDepartment","label":"save-clinicalDepartment"},{"moduleName":"","label":""},{"moduleName":"","label":""}],"name":"診療科聴取","description":"","matchingmethod":1,"type":"drjoy^Text To Speech$Text to speech","params":{"prompt":"","stop_by_dtmf":"No","category_words":""}},"入力_診療科聴取":{"layout":{"x":0,"y":3750},"next":[{"condition":"^TIMEOUT$","label":"timeout","nextModuleName":"リトライ_診療科聴取"},{"condition":"^ERROR$","label":"error","nextModuleName":"リトライ_診療科聴取"},{"condition":"^NO_RESULT$","label":"no_result","nextModuleName":"saveDefault-入力_診療科聴取"},{"condition":"^.+$","label":"success","nextModuleName":"OpenAI_診療科聴取"},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""}],"subs":[{"moduleName":"save-clinicalDepartment","label":"save-clinicalDepartment"},{